title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 r. 202.70.5 - Information on Cases
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 r. 202.70.5 - Information on Cases

State Regulations

Information on future court appearances
and case developments can be found at the court system's eCourts site (
www.nycourts.gov/ecourts
). Neither the
court nor the court
clerk
will be responsible for notifying the parties of
scheduled court appearances, although the court or the court
clerk
may do so at
their discretion. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22
r. 202.70.5. Amended
eff. 1/3/2023. State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
